<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>And if you would like to know why I am not a father --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583000' id='t-583000'>I, who by a miracle have 22 godchildren --</span>
